==Korean==

===Adjective===
'''굳다''' (gudda, gutda) 
# to be [[hard]], [[solid]], [[adamant]]

====Derived terms====
*굳은 [[살]] (gudEun sal) [[callus]], hardened skin 

===Adverb===
'''굳이''' (gudI) 
# [[strongly]], [[firmly]], [[obstinately]]

===Noun===
'''굳''' (gud, gut) 

# (obsolete) [[hole]], [[hollow]], [[pit]], [[cave]] <br> cf. Homographic [[gut]] or [[alimentary canal]] 

====Synonyms====

* [[구덩이]] (gudeongI) 
* [[구멍]] (gumeong)
* [[굴]] (gul)

===Verb===
'''굳다''' (gudda, gutda) 
* (intransitive) to become [[hard]], [[solidify]], [[congeal]]  

====Derived terms====
*[[굳어지다]] (gudEjida) (intransitive) to become [[hard]], [[solidify]], [[congeal]]  
*[[굳히다]] (gudhida) (transitive) to [[harden]], [[solidify]], [[congeal]]  

